snippet.title: TURBO LEAPER SAGE '23 Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Introducing Turbo Leaper with a demo at SAGE '23 on September 1!

TURBO LEAPER game and original characters by Riegelsoft.
SUPER FREAKS by SuperFreaks Dev & KingNormal.
EXTRADIMENSIONAL PORTALHOPPPING theme by Zane Little.
SAGE ‘23 art by P3DRO and RummySM; jingle by R3.

Find great gameplay of the origianl Super Freaks franchise at:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOT8gKgYikRHVPKTk3_9-Hg
